## Environment
- Ubuntu 22.04 LTS (x86_64)
- Splunk Enterprise (Linux amd64)

## Installation
Installed Splunk using dpkg and started service via CLI.

## Searches Performed
- index=*
- failed
- error
- login

## Learnings
- Splunk indexes logs for fast searching
- SPL (Search Processing Language) is used for detection
- SOC teams rely on Splunk to detect brute-force, errors, and anomalies
